description: Oklahoma’s first Indian Tandoori truck is serving up delicious Halal cuisine. With their signature excellent service and talent for crafting the tastiest dishes, every local foodie is loving every bite of Sizzle n Spice. Their menu includes tender kebabs, fluffy naan bread, savory rice pilaf, robustly flavorful curries, succulent chutneys, etc...For all this and more, come try Sizzle n Spice. You are too are sure to be delighted!
name: Sizzle n Spice
